values: Well it's friday, too early for me to be up. But, I am still a little sick but getting better. Going up to my mom's house in a little bit, her wedding is tomorrow. i am the maid of honor, and i haven't finished my speech yet but it's getting their. i am pretty sure it is all going to turn out wonderful.

Well i got back from Gainsvillie late Sunday night. I went their to visit some friends of mine. We had alot of fun. Friends from high schol that i haven't seen in awhile. And now it is Wednesday and I am sick. I have been in bed all day taking Medicane's which i don't like to do but...my mom is getting married this Saturday, so i have to be well for that. Just an update on whats been going on in my world lately.
Well this is my first entry. Don't really know what to say......
